###
### Tornado
###
### To create an actual tornado application you should create a
### <project_name>_private file in the formula directory and source
### '. tornado <project_name>' this will create a virtualenv with the
### name of the project
###

###
### Initialize
###

is_formula_installed && return || formula_init

cd $QUICKNESS_SRC

APP_NAME="tornado"
if [ ! -z "$1" ]; then
    APP_NAME="$1"
fi


###
### Dependencies
###

. $Q/evented_libs
. $Q/python_dev $APP_NAME


###
### Installation
###

pip install tornado


###
### Teardown
###

formula_teardown
